name: Episode 24
headline: Costs of adverse events in Renal Cell Carcinoma.
hosts: Learn from the experts about the costs associated with irAEs in patients treated for Renal Cell Carcinoma. Join our hosts Dr. Afreen Shariff and Dr. Tian Zhang as they discuss with guest experts- medical Oncologists Dr. Daniel Geynisman and Dr. Bradley McGregor, MD.
